      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s in absolute mint condition and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. The interior is spotless and it\u2019s been 100% smoke-free. I\u2019m sad to let it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make the next owner so happy. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
