    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a pristine, museum-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L atmospheric straight-six. This specimen boasts a flawless mechanical pedigree: the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled with Beisan components, rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance, and the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity. The S54\u2019s individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous throttle response, channeled through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. Every bushing is tight, the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, and the engine bay is free of any fluid seepage. Finished in a deep gloss with a perfectly preserved Nappa leather interior, this is a turn-key investment for the discerning driver who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
